      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection justified by comparison to higher-fidelity LES data or experimental turbulence measurements; hemolysis constitutive model sensitivity analysis completed.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected; no LES reference data available for this pump geometry. Hemolysis constitutive model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger power law) sensitivity study shows ±18 % variation across three candidate models. Achieved level 2 below required level 3; model-form uncertainty is the dominant epistemic contributor."
